<bibRefCitation author="Gusenleitner, J." box="[1126,1322,1973,1997]" pageId="7" pageNumber="131" pagination="1353 - 1355" refId="ref4302" refString="Gusenleitner, J. (2006) Calligaster zetteli, eine neue Art von den Philippinen (Hymenoptera: Vespidae: Eumeninae). Linzer biologische Beitrage, 38, 1353 - 1355." type="journal article" year="2006">Gusenleitner, 2006</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
). 12, Head, frontal view. 13, Mesosoma, dorsal view.
