<paragraph blockId="8.[151,1437,151,285]" pageId="8" pageNumber="132">
The synonymy with 
<taxonomicName authorityName="van der Vecht. The" authorityYear="1963" box="[426,538,151,177]" class="Insecta" family="Eumenidae" genus="Pseudozumia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="132" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="gracilis">
<emphasis box="[426,538,151,177]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="132">P. gracilis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, the only 
<taxonomicName authorityName="de Saussure" authorityYear="1875" box="[646,795,151,177]" class="Insecta" family="Eumenidae" genus="Pseudozumia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="132" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[646,795,151,177]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="132">Pseudozumia</emphasis>
